msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:17
msgid ""
"Hovering over one item can open all menu items simultaneously, creating a "
"smooth, unified interaction. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:22
msgid "ScrollSpy"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:23
msgid ""
"Highlight the active section in the menu based on current scroll position — "
"great for one-page layouts and guides. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:29
msgid "Custom Icons, Emojis & Letters"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:30
msgid ""
"Upload your own icons or use emojis and letters for creative, unique, or "
"casual designs. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:36
msgid "Extended Labels & Hold Open"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:37
msgid ""
"Add longer text descriptions and keep label text visible with the “Hold "
"Open” option for clarity and accessibility."
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:43
msgid "Social Sharing"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:44
msgid ""
"Include social sharing links from 30+ services to help users share your "
"content and boost traffic. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:50
msgid "Translate"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:51
msgid "Let visitors translate your website content in real time. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:57
msgid "Print"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:58
msgid ""
"PAdd a quick-access print button that launches the browser print dialog for "
"easy page printing."
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:63
msgid "Next / Previous Post Navigation"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:64
msgid ""
"Automatically link to the next or previous post within the same category to "
"keep visitors engaged and moving through your content."
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:69
msgid "Scroll to Top / Bottom"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:70
msgid ""
"Add one-click scroll links that take users instantly to the top or bottom of "
"the page — ideal for long content pages. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:76
msgid ""
"Include a live search input directly inside the menu, enabling users to "
"quickly find content without leaving the current view. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:82
msgid "Hiding/Showing"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:83
msgid ""
"Allows you to control the visibility of your floating menus based on the "
"user's scroll position on the webpage. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:89
msgid "Scroll-Based Visibility"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:90
msgid ""
"Show the menu after the user scrolls a specific distance, hide it after a "
"defined scroll point, or make it sticky and responsive to scrolling. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:96
msgid "Timer-Based Visibility"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:97
msgid ""
"Delay menu appearance using a display timer, or automatically hide it after "
"a certain number of seconds. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:103
msgid "Activate by URL"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:104
msgid ""
"Display the menu only when the current page URL contains specific keywords "
"or parameters. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:110
msgid "Activate by Referrer URL"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:111
msgid ""
"Trigger menu display based on the visitor’s referrer — useful for targeting "
"traffic from ads or campaigns.  "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:117
msgid "Comprehensive Display Controls"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:118
msgid ""
"Use shortcodes, post types, tags, categories, or archive pages to fine-tune "
"where and when your menu appears. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:124
msgid "Device-Based Visibility"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:125
msgid ""
"Remove the menu entirely on mobile or desktop devices to optimize "
"performance and layout per screen. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:131
msgid "User Role Permissions"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:132
msgid ""
"Restrict menu visibility for specific user roles (e.g., Admins, Editors, "
"Subscribers)."
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:137
msgid "Multilingual Support"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:138
msgid ""
"Show menus based on language preferences. Compatible with WPML and Polylang."
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:143
msgid "Scheduling"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:144
msgid ""
"Schedule menu appearances based on specific days, times, and dates. This "
"allows you to promote temporary events or campaigns without cluttering your "
"website permanently. "
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:150
msgid "Browser Compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: admin/settings/5.pro.php:151
msgid ""
"Ensure your menus display correctly across a wide range of browsers. If "
"necessary, you can choose to hide menus for specific browsers to address "
"compatibility issues with outdated software versions. "
msgstr ""

